## Root Cause Analysis Summary

**Root Cause Service:** `ts-ui-dashboard`

**Key Findings:**
1. The incident involves HTTP POST requests to `http://ts-ui-dashboard:8080/api/v1/inside_pay_service/inside_payment` experiencing SLO violations with HTTP 503 errors
2. ts-ui-dashboard is returning 503 errors (22 occurrences in abnormal data)
3. All downstream services (ts-inside-payment-service, ts-payment-service, ts-order-service) are completing successfully with HTTP 200 status codes
4. The 503 errors originate from ts-ui-dashboard itself, not from downstream service failures
5. ts-ui-dashboard shows no resource constraints (CPU, memory, deployment all healthy)

**Fault Propagation:**
- ts-ui-dashboard generates 503 errors
- loadgenerator (the client making requests) receives these errors

